    "This means that the model may sometimes create offensive or harmful content.",
    "In addition, GPT models cannot fully understand the context and meaning of the generated text and do not perform well in tasks that require the application of logical inference, which is not found in the data that forms the basis of learning (Strubell et al., 2019).",
    "In addition, GPT models are computationally intensive to learn and require large amounts of data and computational resources (Zhou et al., 2021).",
    "Therefore, it is important to be aware of these limitations and use GPT technology responsibly.",
